                "url": "/topics/allow"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/klaus_lackner_747911",
        "quote": "Technologies simmer along before they are feasible. That simmer can be short or long, but then they get traction. And from there to being huge is a couple of decades.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Klaus Lackner",
            "url": "/quotes/klaus_lackner_747911"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Before",
