    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/klaus_lackner_747920",
        "quote": "The fact that companies are getting into building power plants that collect their own CO2 on-site shows there's some leadership in that industry. Some industries have seen the writing on the wall: that carbon will have to be managed.",
