    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/klaus_lackner_747922",
        "quote": "The idea that somewhere in the desert far away you have a CO2 absorber that's removing the CO2 from the air is an attractive one. It's a costly process that many will say is too expensive, but so are fuel cells in cars. It's a matter of political will to move this forward.",
